    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I'm selling my well-loved car, and it has been such a joy to own. It runs beautifully and has been kept in wonderful shape over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable, great-looking vehicle without the 'fresh off the lot' price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come by and take it for a test drive!",
