      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, a testament to balanced performance and enduring quality. This selection features a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience. Each component has been vetted to meet our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and presentation. This is an exceptional opportunity for the professional seeking a dependable, high-caliber motorcar that commands a presence on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
